title: Two trapped in crash
content: Police are at the scene of the crash on Sunday morning (File photo).      Two people are reportedly trapped in cars after a collision on the outskirts of Palmerston North.    The crash happened on a one-way bridge on Turitea Rd, south of Palmerston North, at 9.15am on Sunday, police said.    It was reported a person was trapped in each of the crashed cars.
